<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<?import javafx.scene.chart.PieChart?>
<?import javafx.scene.control.*?>
<?import javafx.scene.image.Image?>
<?import javafx.scene.image.ImageView?>
<?import javafx.scene.layout.*?>
<?import javafx.scene.text.Text?>

<AnchorPane xmlns="http://javafx.com/javafx/24.0.1"
            xmlns:fx="http://javafx.com/fxml/1"
            fx:controller="com.example.wealthwise.Controller.Client.profileController"
            stylesheets="@../../Styles/Dashboard.css"
            prefWidth="900" prefHeight="750"
            styleClass="dashboard">

    <!-- Profile Header -->
    <HBox spacing="15" alignment="CENTER_LEFT" AnchorPane.topAnchor="30.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="20.0">
        <ImageView fx:id="avatarImage" fitWidth="80" fitHeight="80">
            <image>
                <Image url="/Images/profile-user.png"/>
            </image>
        </ImageView>
        <VBox spacing="5">
            <Label fx:id="usernameLabel" text="John Doe" styleClass="section_title"/>
            <Label fx:id="emailLabel" text="johndoe@email.com" styleClass="date_lbl"/>
            <HBox spacing="10">
                <Button fx:id="editProfileBtn" text="Edit Profile"/>
                <Button fx:id="logoutBtn" text="Logout"/>
            </HBox>
        </VBox>
    </HBox>

    <!-- Account Summary -->
    <HBox spacing="15" AnchorPane.topAnchor="130.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="20.0">
        <VBox styleClass="account_view" prefWidth="200" alignment="CENTER">
            <Label text="Total Spent"/>
            <Label fx:id="totalSpentLabel" text="$1,250" styleClass="expense_ammount"/>
        </VBox>
        <VBox styleClass="account_view" prefWidth="200" alignment="CENTER">
            <Label text="Monthly Budget"/>
            <Label fx:id="monthlyBudgetLabel" text="$2,000" styleClass="income_ammount"/>
        </VBox>
        <VBox styleClass="account_view" prefWidth="200" alignment="CENTER">
            <Label text="Savings"/>
            <Label fx:id="savingsLabel" text="$750" styleClass="income_ammount"/>
        </VBox>
    </HBox>

    <!-- Budget Progress -->
    <VBox spacing="5" AnchorPane.topAnchor="230.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="20.0">
        <Label text="Budget Usage" styleClass="section_title"/>
        <ProgressBar fx:id="budgetProgressBar" progress="0.6" prefWidth="600"/>
        <Label fx:id="budgetPercentLabel" text="60%"/>
    </VBox>

    <!-- Charts and Transactions -->
    <HBox spacing="20" AnchorPane.topAnchor="300.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="20.0">
        <VBox spacing="10">
            <Label text="Expense Categories" styleClass="section_title"/>
            <PieChart fx:id="expensePieChart" prefWidth="300" prefHeight="250"/>
        </VBox>
        <VBox spacing="10">
            <Label text="Recent Transactions" styleClass="section_title"/>
            <ListView fx:id="transactionsList" prefHeight="250" styleClass="transaction_listview"/>
            <Button fx:id="viewAllBtn" text="View All"/>
        </VBox>
    </HBox>

    <!-- Quick Actions -->
    <HBox spacing="15" AnchorPane.topAnchor="580.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="20.0">
        <Button fx:id="addExpenseBtn" text="Add Expense"/>
        <Button fx:id="addIncomeBtn" text="Add Income"/>
    </HBox>

    <!-- Settings -->
    <HBox spacing="15" AnchorPane.topAnchor="620.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="20.0">
        <Label text="Dark Mode"/>
        <CheckBox fx:id="darkModeCheckBox"/>
        <Button fx:id="settingsBtn" text="Settings"/>
        <Label fx:id="lastSyncLabel" text="Last synced: 10 mins ago"/>
    </HBox>

</AnchorPane>
